messages.message: Hi team, we have a customer evaluating us who's looking to extract from tables. I'm having some difficulties accurately extracting all rows on this table. This has previously worked using "extract all tables", and that prompt no longer captures this specific one. Am now trying the prompt "extract all payment summary tables" and it grabs the correct table, but misses the bottom 4 rows. (Table extraction toggled). Any advice here?
Extract all tables works in Converse but not Build. Accurately grabs the table I'm looking for
